  "privacyPolicyTitle": "Àdánwò Policy",
  "privacyLastUpdated": "Imudojuiwọn to kẹhin: Oṣu Kẹta 2025",
  "privacyIntro": "At {appName}, your Àdánwò is paramount. This Àdánwò Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal and health-related data. By using our services, you agree to the practices described below.",
  "privacySectionDataCollection": "1. Gbigba data",
  "privacyDataCollectionBody": "We collect the following categories of data: • Personal Information: NOrúkọ Imẹeli address, Fọọnu number, Deeti of birth, and gender. • Ilera Data: Blood type, aÀlẹ́sẹ́ chronic conditions, mOogun vital signs, symptom logs, and Triage results. • Iṣẹ́-ní-bẹ̀bẹ̀ Contacts: Names, Fọọnu numbers, and relationships of your designated contacts. • Device Data: Device type, operating system, and app version for compatibility and sÀtìlẹ́yìn • Usage Data: Feature interactions and anonymized analytics to improve our services. We only collect data that is necessary for providing our Ilera companion services. You have full control over what information you provide.",
  "privacySectionDataStorage": "2. Data ipamọ & ìsekóòdù",
  "privacyDataStorageBody": "Your data is stored using industry-leading security measures:\n\n• Encryption at Rest: All data stored in our databases is encrypted using AES-256 encryption.\n• Encryption in Transit: All data transmitted between your device and our servers uses TLS 1.3 encryption.\n• Health Passport: Your health passport data is encrypted with a unique key derived from your credentials.\n• Koodu QR Sharing: Shared health data via QR codes is encrypted and time-limited.\n• Infrastructure: Our servers are hosted in SOC 2 Type II certified data centers with 24/7 monitoring.\n\nWe do not store payment card information. All payment processing is handled by certified third-party providers.",
  "privacySectionGdpr": "3. GDPR Ibamu",
  "privacyGdprBody": "{appName} is fully compliant with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR): • Lawful Basis: We process your data based on your explicit consent and contractual necessity. • Data Minimization: We only collect and process data that is strictly necessary. • Purpose Limitation: Your data is used only for the purposes for which it was collected. • Right to Access: You can request a complete copy of your personal data at any tÀkókò • Right to Rectification: You can update or correct your data through the app sẸ̀yìn • Right to Erasure: You can request complete deletion of your account and data. • Right to Portability: You can Jade your data in a machine-readable format. • Data Processing Agreements: Gbogbo third-party processors have signed DPAs. • Cross-Border Transfers: Data is processed within the EU/EEA unless explicit consent is given otherwise.",
  "privacySectionYourRights": "4. Awọn ẹtọ rẹ",
  "privacyRightsBody": "You have the following rights regarding your data: • Access: View Gbogbo your personal and Ilera data within the app or request a data eJade • Correction: Ṣatunṣe your Alaye information at any Àkókò through Ṣatunṣe PAlaye • Deletion: Request account deletion through Ẹ̀yìn > Data & Àdánwò > Paarẹ Account. • Restriction: Limit how certain data is processed by adjusting your notification and sharing preferences. • Objection: Object to specific data processing activities by contacting our Data Protection Officer. • Withdrawal of Consent: You may withdraw consent at any Àkókò without affecting the lawfulness of prior processing. To exercise any of these rights, contact us at privacy@vitalseker.com or through the in-app Àtìlẹ́yìn feature.",
  "privacySectionContactUs": "5. Kan si wa",
  "privacyContactBody": "If you have any questions or concerns Nipa this Àdánwò Policy or our data practices, please contact us: • EImẹeli privacy@vitalseker.com • SÀtìlẹ́yìn support@vitalseker.com • Data Protection Officer: dpo@vitalseker.com • Address: {producer}, Data Protection Office We aim to respond to Gbogbo privacy-related inquiries within 30 days.",
